---
const testimonials = [
  {
    name: 'Antony',
    description: 'Lead dev @ Lormas studio',
    image: 'https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/921368997482602536/0627033cd145e945f0992dae839729fc.png?size=1024',
    message:
      '“As a partner of Cloudcode, I always appreciate all aspects of service quality. For me, choosing Cloudcode is the right decision. The server operates stably, the price is extremely reasonable, the support team is dedicated and thoughtful. we are comitted to continue using Cloudcode\'s service for a long time.”',
  },
  {
    name: 'Cụt (penguin.txt)',
    description: 'User',
    image: 'https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1397959209957458201/3c618ec3243338340fee0195a447c15e.png?size=1024',
    message:
      '“Minecraft server at cloudcode bring a really good gaming experience for me, even with 2gb ram and 1 core, mine minecraft server still run fine with 5 players with geyser and floodgate”',
  },
  {
    name: 'mkshustov',
    description: 'User',
    image: 'https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/695544452101570560/f3cc3959a7ebe9821a38b663512ea434.png?size=1024',
    message:
      '“ I want to say that this is an excellent stable hosting service. It seems to me that only here you can write to the owner every day and get an answer :)”',
